Verification Commands
Check files:
Shellls -lh outputls -lh output/publicls -lh output/playlistsShow more lines
Check database counts:
Shellsqlite3 omega.db "SELECT provider_kind, COUNT(*) FROM provider_channels GRO*P BY provider_kind;"*qlite* omega.db "SELECT COUNT(*) FROM channels;"sqlite3 omega.db "SELECT COUNT(*) FROM programmes;"``*Show more lines
Check XMLTV:
Shell*ython**- <<'PY'*rom*pathlib import Path*ext*=*Path("output/omega.xml").read_text*)*t*= chr(60)*mp*=*chr(38)print*"*eal XML declaration:", text.starts*ith(lt + "?xml"))*rint*"escaped XML declaration:", text.s*artswith(amp + "lt*?xml"))*rint*"*eal programme count:", text.count(*t + "programme"))*rint*"*scaped programme count:", text.cou*t(amp + "lt;programme"))PY**`*Show more lines
Expected:
Plain Text*eal*XML*declaration: Trueescaped*XML*declaration: False*scaped*programme*count: 0``*Show more lines
Check playlist URL escaping:
Shell*rep*"^*ttp"*output/omega.m3u | grep "&amp;" | *eadShow more lines
